OL,3,CResidents in Spain can now block
OL,4,Choliday rentals under new law
OL,6,FHoliday-makers travelling to Spain
OL,7,Fthis summer may have fewer
OL,8,Faccommodation choices due to a new law
OL,9,Fallowing residents to block holiday
OL,10,Frentals in their buildings.
OL,12,FThe Spanish government has launched a
OL,13,Fcrackdown on holiday rentals as part
OL,14,Fof new measures to prioritise
OL,15,Ffunctional housing for the local
OL,16,Fcommunities.
