OL,3,CResidents in Spain can now block
OL,4,Choliday rentals under new law
OL,6,FUnder the new law, which came into
OL,7,Feffect on April 3, property owners in
OL,8,Fapartment blocks can bar others from
OL,9,Fusing their apartments as holiday lets
OL,10,Fby way of a majority vote.
OL,12,FTo enforce the new rules, 60% of
OL,13,Fneighbours need to vote against the
OL,14,Fintroduction of a holiday let in their
OL,15,Fbuilding on the grounds of noise
OL,16,Fconcerns and disruption.
