OL,3,CResidents in Spain can now block
OL,4,Choliday rentals under new law
OL,6,FSpain's housing ministry told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "We have empowered neighbours to
OL,8,Fdecide whether or not to open an
OL,9,Fapartment as a holiday let in their
OL,10,Fcommunity of owners.
OL,12,F"This government believes in the
OL,13,Fsocial function of housing, which is
OL,14,Fenshrined in the Constitution, and
OL,15,Fwhich prioritises residential use over
OL,16,Fother uses."
