OL,3,CResidents in Spain can now block
OL,4,Choliday rentals under new law
OL,6,FSpain's Prime Minister Pedro Sanchez
OL,7,Fhas also focused attention on "high-
OL,8,Ftension areas," introducing a cap on
OL,9,Fthe number of rentals allowed in
OL,10,Fpopular cities.
OL,12,FThe new laws are in response to a huge
OL,13,Fsurge in house prices and rent, with
OL,14,Fsome estate agents last year citing a
OL,15,F24% rise in the last five years.
OL,17,FMr Sanchez blames foreign buyers and,
OL,18,Fin January, announced plans to impose
OL,19,Fa 100% tax on homes bought in the
OL,20,Fcountry by non-EU residents.
