OL,3,CResidents in Spain can now block
OL,4,Choliday rentals under new law
OL,6,FThe rising prices haven't gone
OL,7,Funnoticed among residents either; this
OL,8,Fmonth, Spain saw protests across 40
OL,9,Fcities to demand lower rents and
OL,10,Ftighter restrictions on holiday
OL,11,Frentals.
OL,13,FAccording to Finder, in 2023,
OL,14,Fapproximately 17.81 million British
OL,15,Ftourists visited Spain, making it the
OL,16,Fmost popular travel destination by far
OL,17,Fthat year.
